1. Get All Users

GET http://localhost:8081/client/user

2. Get User by ID

GET http://localhost:8081/client/user/{id}

3. Create New User

POST http://localhost:8081/client/user

Request:

  {
        "name": "surya",
        "age": 50,
        "salary": 40000.0
    }
    


4. Update Existing User

PUT http://localhost:8081/client/user/{id}

Request:

{
        "id": 5,
        "name": "surya",
        "age": 50,
        "salary": 50000.0
    }
    

5. Delete User by ID

DELETE http://localhost:8081/client/user/{id}

6. Delete All Users

DELETE http://localhost:8080/user

7. Get Users with Pagination and Filter

GET http://localhost:8081/client/user/page?pageNo=0&pageSize=5&sortBy=name&minSalary=30000
